Version 0.2:
Support for dynamic memory values is implemented (constructors-only).
+ use 'pidof' to get the game process pid
+ removed libgcheater dependency
+ added '~/.ugtrain/' config search path
+ added float support
+ added "Chromium B.S.U." example for dyn. mem.

Version 0.1:
Support for static memory values is implemented.
Support for universal checks is implemented.
